 
 1.SORT
 
 cat >>demo.txt
 
Jenny
Abhi
Pavan
Kalyan
Bruno

sort demo.txt --> for text

Abhi
Bruno
Jenny
Kalyan
Pavan

sort -n demo.txt ---> for numbers

sort -r demo.txt -->Sorts data in reverse order (descending)

Pavan
Kalyan
Jenny
Bruno
Abhi

sort -nr number.txt -->Sorts a file with numeric data in reverse order

sort -u demo.txt --> Sorts and removes duplicate lines, providing a unique sorted list

sort -m monthfile.txt: Sorts by month names.

Febrauary
May
March
June
August
------------------------------------------------------------------------

2.SHUTDOWN:

shutdown -->shutdowns the system

shutdown -c --> to cancel the Shutdown
 
 

